message: King County Council launched a campaign with several partners to draw attention to labor and sex trafficking and help victims find resources.

data.description: King County Council is launching a campaign, with several partners, to raise public awareness for labor and sex trafficking, and help victims find resources. data.title: King County Council announces human trafficking awareness campaign
